{"tid":193324,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"二戰時期 日軍殺國軍既人多d定共產黨既人多","createTime":"2017-04-09T08:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T15:28:50.000Z","uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a080eb7336a15db44c8ad2cba71132728614b0c","tid":193324,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"假設個陣真係屠殺左南京三十萬人<br />\n咁到底係邊一邊既人傷得多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有謠言話個陣共匪隱藏左唔少實力 推曬國軍去對抗，咁理應國軍應該傷得重d 應該更加仇日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但而家睇翻 台灣人十分崇日，完全唔覺得日本人曾經對佢地前人做過d咁既事，而趕走國民黨既共匪就不斷喺大陸擴大仇日思想<br />\n咁到底日軍殺得邊d人多先會引起咁既局面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然，台灣人咁崇日都有原因係因為日本曾經管治過佢地啦，但假設個陣日軍係隊左好多國軍，咁國民黨當日敗走到台灣唔係更應該散播仇日思想咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac885386f547efe835a12d1ef708038168eb0a71","tid":193324,"uid":4246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"共產黨殺人多啲"},{"pid":"eb10636ce295ba0f5caf301c7e5906abbe968ff6","tid":193324,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:32:18.000Z","msg":"國民黨管治台灣仲腐敗過日治時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bbfad2175522e98f93c88aa3e9a4defc170dbd","tid":193324,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"關咩殺殺殺事, 而家新一代冇經歷過戰爭, <br />\n<br />\n日本而家發展得又好, 國民質素又好, 台灣人咪鐘意佢地囉, <br />\n<br />\n中國要同日本爭釣島, 咪不斷掀起國民仇日囉, <br />\n<br />\n但中國人咪又係咁鐘意去日本旅行, 用日本貨, 口嫌體正直"},{"pid":"b37e0bd545dd97b6b147d5cfc86f2fae77e8da4f","tid":193324,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國民黨管治台灣仲腐敗過日治時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n禁言個段時期睇翻wiki都覺得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2162acc0f9cc3162ab4c667b8c7063534202e3b9","tid":193324,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關咩殺殺殺事, 而家新一代冇經歷過戰爭, <br />\n<br />\n日本而家發展得又好, 國民質素又好, 台灣人咪鐘意佢地囉, <br />\n<br />\n中國要同日本爭釣島, 咪不斷掀起國民仇日囉, <br />\n<br />\n但中國人咪又係咁鐘意去日本旅行, 用日本貨, 口嫌體正直</blockquote><br />\n一定唔止 如果真係只係關尖閣諸島事 <br />\n點解安倍去靖國神社參拜又可以令共匪咁敏感，慰安婦事件同尖閣諸島係兩回事喎"},{"pid":"3f9f088571a1db53081ab2c124475a1573a43b9c","tid":193324,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共產黨殺人多啲</blockquote><br />\n啫係南京大屠殺係共匪功勞？"},{"pid":"49f6a9073cd904df0ebbc62f245006f3dd499320","tid":193324,"uid":4246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>共產黨殺人多啲</blockquote><br />\n啫係南京大屠殺係共匪功勞？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.storm.mg/article/76808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F76808&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=638f68da\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.storm.mg/article/76808</a>"},{"pid":"858acb2b4dcca31eacb64ca2028dc10e1f978099","tid":193324,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國民黨管治台灣仲腐敗過日治時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n禁言個段時期睇翻wiki都覺得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戒嚴時期同共產黨冇分別，好多異見者都比政府冤枉係共產黨員，甚至比警察捉走後一去冇回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5436a7a3919308c6125778747b65b6a841b689f","tid":193324,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><b